OL,6,FOn Thursday at London's Wood Green
OL,7,FCrown Court, they were sentenced to a
OL,8,Ftotal of 25 years and five months'
OL,9,Fimprisonment after previously pleading
OL,10,Fguilty to fraud and money laundering-
OL,11,Frelated offences.
OL,13,FThe judge warned them they are all
OL,14,Fliable to be deported after servicing
OL,15,Ftheir sentences and added that "an
OL,16,Fenormous amount of work" by the
OL,17,FDepartment for Work and Pensions (DWP)
OL,18,Fhad to be carried out in order to
OL,19,Fprosecute the gang.
