OL,6,FInvestigators even discovered three
OL,7,F"benefit factories" in London, the CPS
OL,8,Fsaid, claiming to help people get a
OL,9,Fnational insurance number using "claim
OL,10,Fpacks" containing forged and false
OL,11,Fdocuments.
OL,13,FThe gang would also give the claimants
OL,14,Ftips on how to fool the system, the
OL,15,Fcourt heard.
OL,17,FBut after applicants made their
OL,18,Fclaims, they left them in the hands of
OL,19,Fthe gang who laundered money through a
OL,20,Fnumber of different accounts.
